		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">首屆 奮興會 第5講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/100">古約翰先生</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=0">首屆</a>
